reviewText: Very well done! Not your typical "reality show".. no drama, no back-stabbing, etc. Just a true look at what it's like attending a vet school. I shared with my daughter and granddaughter - they enjoyed it, too. Highly recommend!

Very Informative and interesting DVD that helped me to see what I'm getting into going into Vet School! I love all the episodes and I'd recommend this to anyone considering a career in Veterinary Medicine!
Grand daughter going to be veteranarian and loved these DVD's
